    <h1>Anchor Text</h1>
    <p class="description">The clickable text in a hyperlink. Google has used anchor text as a ranking signal since the original PageRank algorithm — pages with keyword-rich anchors in their backlinks <strong>consistently rank higher</strong>, but overdo it and Penguin steps in.</p>
